<b>What's new:</b>
<p>
<ul>
<li>modified climate model to fix problems with ELA location
<li>fixed bug in ice visualization that caused the sim to hang for glaciers less than 80m long
<li>fixed some debris that we getting stuck on the valley floor
</ul>
<p>
<b>Known problems:</b>
<ul>
<li>when ELA is below terminus, the drawn ELA jumps around a bit when the terminus reaches the ELA
</ul>
<p>
<b>Not implemented:</b>
<ul>
<li>snowfall is not visible
<li>can't switch between English and metric units
<li>time-based graphs are not implemented
<li>"Steady State" button doesn't advance clock time
<li>features need to be split into Intro, Advanced, and Climate Experiments panels
<li>interface for climate experiments is not implemented
</ul>
